# Exclude all subdirectories (repositories)
*/

# Include management files
!.gitignore
!ECOSYSTEM.md
!ecosystem-manager.sh
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
# Re-include nested paths too (same pitfall as .github below): the leading
# */ rule also matches subdirectories such as .claude/skills, so a single
# !.claude/ is not enough.
!.claude/
!.claude/**
# ...but keep session-local Claude Code files out
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# Exception: Include docs directory for ecosystem documentation
!docs/

# Exception: Include .github (workflows, scripts, settings) for this repo
# Re-include nested paths too: the leading */ rule also matches subdirectories
# such as .github/workflows, so a single !.github/ is not enough.
!.github/
!.github/**

# macOS system files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*

# Editor files
*.swp
*.swo
*~